room_title: Escape room "Jungle Game" by Maze Rooms in Los Angeles
room_address: 1147 S Robertson Blvd Los Angeles, CA 90035
room_description: In the midst of a jungle, things are not always as they seem. As if you are just pieces in a giant board game... Mysteries and intrigues are around every corner. Get ready to roll the dice and think quickly to get through this ordeal to make it back to your own world! But be careful: if you don't finish the game in 60 minutes, you'll get lost in the jungle forever.
